	loading_dst10_unsigned = "Celebrate ten years of surviving the Constant!",
	loading_eyeofthestorm_trailer = "Few things can set the Queen of the Constant herself on edge...",
	loading_farming = "The days have been filled with tilling and toil,\nGathering seeds and nourishing soil,\nIn hopes that the crops will produce at their best,\n(Just make sure that you keep a sharp eye out for pests!)",
	loading_farming2 = "Not everyone has a talent for farming.",
	loading_feast = "The food is prepared, the table is set,\nGather round for a feast that you won't soon forget.",
	loading_gameplay_trailer = "The future might be daunting,\n(The present's scary too)\nBut if the past has taught us anything,\nTogether, we'll get through.",
	loading_gingersnow = "When the air grows colder and snow covers the ground, a gingerbread village can sometimes be found.",
	loading_gnarwail = "The sea poses many dangers, one must always be prepared for rough waters.",
	loading_goats_victorian = "\"Always hold the board steady. Remember, a sharp knife is safer than a dull one.\nDon't forget.\"",
	loading_goosemoose_yule = "A large plump goose sounds fit for a feast,\nUnless you're the meal for the terrible beast.",
	loading_grotto = "You won't be able to run forever.",
	loading_grotto2 = "The Lunar Island wasn't the only consequence of the moon fragment's impact into the sea. It also revealed a part of the caves long since sealed away and forgotten. One might wonder if landing on that spot was really a coincidence...",
	loading_lunacy = "Open your mind to terrifying new possibilities.",
	loading_magma = "Battlemaster Pugna draws great pleasure in subjecting combatants to the whims of his Battlearena forged of stone and fire.",
	loading_magma2 = "To escape the fiery Forge, our Survivors must triumph in battle against Battlemaster Pugna's fearsome champions.",
	loading_march_qol = "It's the thought that counts.",
	loading_maxwell = "Maxwell's extended reign on the Nightmare Throne altered him in ways that are not yet fully understood. He continues to rely heavily on his tome, the Codex Umbra, as a result.",
	loading_maxwell2 = "Maxwell grew quite accustomed to a world that followed his rules... but now someone else is pulling the strings.",
	loading_merm = "Merms inhabited the marshes of The Constant long before humans, and will probably exist long after.",
	loading_newhorizons = "The path ahead is long and treacherous, but you've come too far to turn back now.",
	loading_pig_elite = "The Pig King's four elite warriors give half their winnings to those poor unfortunate pigs with no mud to roll in.",
	loading_pigking = "Legend has it the Pig King and his followers left their home long ago to rule freely in The Constant.",
	loading_pirates1 = "If you wish to sail the open sea, best beware the pirates of Moon Quay!",
	loading_roadmap = "Could there be light at the end of the tunnel?",
	loading_roadmap2 = "Survivors that dared to make camp on the lunar island often claim to have been visited by strange apparitions.",
	loading_terraria_trailer = "One teensy little mishap has plunged the world of Terraria into rather... constant danger, and is terrarizing the Constant like nothing before! Who knows what might slip through the cracks when two worlds collide?",
	loading_walter_trailer = "Friendship can be found in the most unlikely places.",
	loading_walter_trailer2 = "On a night like this, one doesn't want to travel alone.",
	loading_wanda1 = "Traveling back and forth through time gets disorienting after a while. Trying to remember the events of multiple timelines can make one appear a bit scatterbrained.",
	loading_wanda_trailer = "Wanda has been trying to outrun her future for longer than she can remember - but after a split-second decision left her tangled up in the Constant's timestream, it might be her past that's finally catching up to her...",
	loading_warly2_trailer = "There are some memories that never leave you.\nFor Warly, they are the smell of an old family recipe, and the warmth of his dear Maman's hugs.",
	loading_warly_trailer = "Warly will never give up hope that he'll see the sweet smile of his dear Maman again.",
	loading_waterlogged = "These towering oceanic trees might offer a moment of respite from the dangers of the open sea, but nowhere in the Constant is truly safe for long.",
	loading_waterlogged_trailer = "Sailing beneath the comforting shade of the Drift Wood's Great Tree, it's all too easy to forget the danger that dangles above.",
	loading_webber = "Webber could have easily seen his unique predicament as an affliction or a curse. Instead, he's chosen to view it as a second chance, and one that he fully intends not to waste.",
	loading_webber2 = "These days, Webber doesn't have to go far to find a friend.",
	loading_webber_feast = "\"We're super excited to watch everyone open the presents we got them.\"",
	loading_webber_sad = "Listen well children, and mind the warnings of your parents... naughtiness always comes back to bite you in the end.",
	loading_webber_trailer = "Some things simply can't be undone.",
	loading_wendy = "Wendy clings fiercely to the grief over her sister's death, for fear that moving on would cause Abigail's memory to fade.",
	loading_wendy_blogpostart = "\"I know you're still there, Abigail... we'll be able to play together again soon.\"",
	loading_wendy_creepy = "She can't escape her monomaniacal obsession with death.\nNeither can you.",
	loading_wendy_trailer = "Abigail could always find a way to bring a smile to Wendy's face... sadly, she would later become the reason it went away for good.",
	loading_wendy_trailer2 = "Fond memories...",
	loading_wendy_victorian = "Wendy finds a strange comfort in elaborate mourning rituals.\nIt takes the guesswork out of grieving.",
	loading_wes1 = "Wes often gets carried away while performing his ballonomantic arts.",
	loading_wes_trailer = "Trying to explain this mime's psyche would be a fool's errand... an April one, in fact.",
