	loading_wes_victorian = "There are few more satisfying feelings in life than knowing one's work is done for the day.",
	loading_wickerbottom = "Delightfully, Ms. Wickerbottom has found her passion for the written word has only deepened as the years go by. Any knowledge committed to paper becomes impervious to the brain fogs of age, you know!",
	loading_wickerbottom_victorian = "It's a well-known fact that a group of crows is called a \"murder\".\nIt is a lesser known fact that they hold crow funerals.",
